text: Schaanwald is a village of Liechtenstein. It is in the municipality of Mauren. ==Geography== The village is in north-central Liechtenstein. It is on the main road that links Liechtenstein with Buchs, Switzerland and Feldkirch, Austria. ==Notable people== *Melitta Marxer == Gallery == File:Zollamt Feldkirch Tisis .JPG|Customs building File:Haltestelle Schaanwald-East1.jpg|Schaanwald railway station File:Schaanwald Kapelle.jpg|Chapel of Therese von Lisieux ==Other websites== Category:Villages in Liechtenstein
